  "detailed_description": "You are drastically separated from your family in a scary forest with dangerous creatures, and you have to find them again!<br><br>Ratyrinth is a retro, cute and challenging precision platformer, where you have several paths and obstacles to reach your goal.<br>With each level the difficulty increases, adding new mechanics and enemies.<br><br>Simple mechanics like<br>- Run, Jump, Stick to the wall, Climb and Swim.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421910/extras/44ff42d69012fc016477a2324632639a.poster.avif?t=1749757923\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421910/extras/44ff42d69012fc016477a2324632639a.webm?t=1749757923\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421910/extras/44ff42d69012fc016477a2324632639a.mp4?t=1749757923\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Unlockable color palettes:<br>- One unlocked for people sensitive to white light.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421910/extras/f6662671ceb7e72c983787e4e272250c.poster.avif?t=1749757923\" width=600 height=215 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421910/extras/f6662671ceb7e72c983787e4e272250c.webm?t=1749757923\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
